name: LSDoge
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
LSDoge is a new Meme token that offers abundant returns by combining the power of LSD and the master of Meme. By holding $LSDoge, you become a guardian of the Ethereum network and earn sufficient ETH rewards. 

What makes your project unique?
Through a partnership with 0xACID.com, the largest LSDfi project on Arbitrum with over 5000 ETH treasury, LSDoge solves trust risks and can stably generate ETH returns from a large amount of LSD assets in the long run.

History of your project.
LSDoge is incubated by toxinlab, which has many successful projects, such as 0xacid.com

What’s next for your project?
Expanding the user base and providing more value to users

What can your token be used for?
Stake LSDoge token to get high ETH rewards
